PortSystem 1.0

name             httptunnel
version          3.3
categories       net
platforms        darwin
maintainers      gmail.com:izonov

description      Tunnel over HTTP
long_description httptunnel creates a bidirectional virtual data connection \
    tunnelled in HTTP requests. The HTTP requests can be sent via an HTTP \
    proxy if so desired.

homepage         http://www.nocrew.org/software/httptunnel.html
master_sites     ftp://ftp.nocrew.org/pub/nocrew/unix/ \
    http://www.nocrew.org/software/httptunnel/

